Enter Hybrid Animals, the ultimate animal fusion game where you can mix animals to create powerful hybrid creatures and dominate a massive open world RPG! - Multiplayer and Offline Game Modes: Play solo in offline mode or team up with friends in a multiplayer adventure. Explore, fight monsters, and complete quests together!
